-- ENRC Close to Agreement to Buy Out Gertler, Sunday Times Reports
-- B y   J o h n   G l o v e r
-- 2012-07-22T10:21:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-22/enrc-close-to-agreement-to-buy-out-gertler-sunday-times-reports.html
Eurasian Natural Resources Plc, the
U.K.-traded mining company, is close to an agreement on buying
out Dan Gertler, the owner of a 49.5 percent stake in a copper
mine in  Democratic Republic  of Congo, the  Sunday Times  said,
without saying how it got the information.  The agreement may be announced within a month, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
John Glover in London at 
